				\begin{document}$$\hbox {H}_2\,\hbox {O}_2$$\end{document}, acetone, TATP, Sarin, VX, etc. In particular, a recent study showed that it is possible to detect the hepatitis B and C viruses label-free at a wavelength of around 6 μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
